   3. 由于我把入学考试考砸了，所以我没有希望进入法学院学习了。
   4.  You  really put me on the spot by asking me to apologize before so
   many people.
   5. Come on! Be serious, you can't run more fast than Liuxiang at all.
   6. No biggie, it is not surprise for me to fail again.
   
   
